A Machine Learning Algorithm is a mathematical method that learns patterns from data and makes predictions.

Simple Example

Suppose we have email data:

| Email Text       | Result   |
| ---------------- | -------- |
| Win ₹10,000 now  | Spam     |
| Meeting at 5 PM  | Not Spam |
| Free Offer Today | Spam     |

The ML algorithm studies these examples and learns:

"Words like Win, Free, Offer often appear in Spam emails."

When a new email arrives:

"Free Mobile Offer"

The algorithm predicts:

Spam ✅

========

